{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/gaevents/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Ian Chu"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"2befcafc-1603-5374-b4ce-16af77febe57","excerpt":"Google analytics 是一個追蹤數據的好工具，其中有個重要的功能『事件追蹤』，事件追蹤可以讓我們紀錄使用者的動作，例如點擊註冊會員按鈕、影片播放，或是 滾動畫面等等，只要動作能判斷都可，甚至連滑鼠移動可以追蹤。 通常一個網站一定會有要求的 KPI…","html":"<p>Google analytics 是一個追蹤數據的好工具，其中有個重要的功能『事件追蹤』，事件追蹤可以讓我們紀錄使用者的動作，例如點擊註冊會員按鈕、影片播放，或是 滾動畫面等等，只要動作能判斷都可，甚至連滑鼠移動可以追蹤。</p>\n<p>通常一個網站一定會有要求的 KPI，例如註冊會員數、訂單數、填表數等等，這時候如果沒有建立轉換目標的話，就只能看流量自圓其說了 ，下廣告也只能盲目亂打一通。</p>\n<p>這時候就可以使用 google analytics 提供的方法 ga(‘send’, ‘event’, xx , xx , xx)針對這些動作來產生事件，成功產生事件後，就可以再把這個事件設定為轉換目標，就可以做到註冊會員、填表等等的追蹤了。</p>\n<p>但實際上負責 ga 的多半都是行銷，技術人員可能不懂怎設定 ga 事件，又或是沒有配置技術人員，這時候必須要自己來實作了。其實基本的事件追蹤並不難，後面就來教你怎麼自己寫追蹤事件。</p>\n<h2>Google analytics 設定事件</h2>\n<p>首先來教你設定 ga 的事件，下方的官方文件，很清楚的介紹 ga 事件是如何運作的，當 ga(send,{hitType: ‘event’,xxx })執行之後，搭配 hitType 為 event，再加上必備的參數，事件類別以及事件動作，就可以讓 google analytics 接收到資料。下面程式是簡單的事件執行的方法(Method)。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>開發者文件 : <a href=\"https://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/analyticsjs/events?hl=zh-cn\" title=\"google analytics event 技術文件\">google analytics event 技術文件 </a></li>\n<li>說明 : <a href=\"https://support.google.com/analytics/answer/1033068\" title=\"ga 事件中文說明\">ga 事件說明 </a></li>\n</ul>\n<br/>\n簡單介紹一下在寫啥米\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">  <span class=\"token comment\">//當使用者觸發 會發送 類別:導覽清單 ,動作:點擊 ,標籤:註冊會員 , 價值:200</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">ga</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'send'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">hitType</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'event'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">eventCategory</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'導覽清單'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 類別 字元(必填)</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">eventAction</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'點擊'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//動作 字元(必填)</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">eventLabel</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'註冊會員'</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//標籤 字元(選填)</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">eventValue</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'200'</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//標籤 數字(選填)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// ==> 下方為簡化</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">ga</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'send'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'event'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'導覽清單'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'點擊'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'首頁 - 註冊會員'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">200</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<br/>\n<p>寫好了 event 的參數之後，再來是要如何才能觸發，我們預期使用者點擊註冊跟登入會員按鈕，執行 ga 的事件紀錄。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">  <span class=\"token comment\">// 登入註冊會員按鈕</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// 1.html onclick 設定方法</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>button onclick<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"ga('send', 'event', '導覽清單', '點擊', '登入會員');\"</span> id<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"loginMember\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"btn btn-primary\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>登入會員<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>button<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>button onclick<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"ga('send', 'event', '導覽清單', '點擊', '註冊會員', 200);\"</span> id<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"registerMember\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"btn btn-warning\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>註冊會員<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>button<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// 2.不能動到html的話 就用這個方法</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// javascript track click</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>button id<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"loginMember\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"btn btn-primary\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>登入會員<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>button<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>button id<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"registerMember\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"btn btn-warning\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>註冊會員<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>button<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">//確保html載入後執行</span>\n  window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"DOMContentLoaded\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//監聽登入按鈕點擊 執行ga的方法 id=\"loginMember\"</span>\n    document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'#loginMember'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'click'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token function\">ga</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'send'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'event'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'導覽清單'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'點擊'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'登入會員'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//監聽註冊按鈕 id=\"register\"</span>\n    document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'#register'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'click'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token function\">ga</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'send'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'event'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'導覽清單'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'點擊'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'註冊會員'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">200</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token operator\">...</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>實作測試</h2>\n<p>很簡單的做出兩顆按鈕，點擊下方按鈕就會發出 ga event 的方法，就可以讓我們在 ga 上看到數據了，點選 即時 => 事件 來檢查有沒有成功，行為 => 事件 則需要幾小時資料才會出現。</p>\n<div style=\"background:#eee;padding:15px;text-align:center;\">\ndemo:\n  <button id=\"loginMember\" class=\"pure-button pure-button-primary\">登入會員</button>  <button id=\"registerMember\" class=\"pure-button pure-button-primary\">註冊會員</button>\n</div>\n<script>\n  window.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", function() {\n    document.querySelector('#loginMember').addEventListener('click',function(e){\n      alert('觸發 ga event 登入')\n      ga('send', 'event', '導覽清單', '點擊', '登入會員');\n    });\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">document.querySelector('#registerMember').addEventListener('click',function(e){\n  alert('觸發 ga event 註冊')\n  ga('send', 'event', '導覽清單', '點擊', '註冊會員', 200);\n});</code></pre></div>\n<p>}, false);\n</script></p>\n<p>查看 ga 即時是否有數據，發現成功看到數字了，大功告成！\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 7vw 0;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c20944daf49c8941123539f2f3014e6d/acfc1/ga%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82event.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 36.96969696969697%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/c20944daf49c8941123539f2f3014e6d/a805d/ga%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82event.webp 495w,\n/static/c20944daf49c8941123539f2f3014e6d/6ec60/ga%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82event.webp 800w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/c20944daf49c8941123539f2f3014e6d/b3db0/ga%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82event.png 495w,\n/static/c20944daf49c8941123539f2f3014e6d/acfc1/ga%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82event.png 800w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/c20944daf49c8941123539f2f3014e6d/acfc1/ga%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82event.png\"\n            alt=\"ga即時event\"\n            title=\"ga即時event\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">ga即時event</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<br/>\n<h2>ga event 產生器</h2>\n<p>最後順便寫了 ga event 產生器，如果你不太會改參數的話，直接用下來複製貼上吧，只差我沒加上取消互動的參數，還有表單沒特別設計有點醜醜。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>連結 : <a href=\"https://work.ianccy.com/gaeventgenerator.html\" title=\"ga event generator\">ga event generator </a></li>\n</ul>\n<iframe height='700' scrolling='no' src=\"https://work.ianccy.com/gaeventgenerator.html\" frameborder='no' allowtransparency='true' allowfullscreen='true' style='width: 100%;'>\n</iframe>\n<h2>Google analytics 事件設定目標轉換</h2>\n<p>官方文件有關於轉換的不同設定教學，我們這邊利用剛剛建立好的事件來設定轉換，接下來就只剩下設定目標轉換，點選左下角的管理員 => 點選目標 => 新增目標 => 自訂。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>文件 : <a href=\"https://support.google.com/analytics/answer/1032415\" title=\"ga 官方目標設定\">ga 官方目標設定 </a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 7vw 0;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d3400496199bdfb0b116a0bd14ba040a/acfc1/%E8%BD%89%E6%8F%9B%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 81.41414141414141%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/d3400496199bdfb0b116a0bd14ba040a/a805d/%E8%BD%89%E6%8F%9B%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A.webp 495w,\n/static/d3400496199bdfb0b116a0bd14ba040a/6ec60/%E8%BD%89%E6%8F%9B%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A.webp 800w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/d3400496199bdfb0b116a0bd14ba040a/b3db0/%E8%BD%89%E6%8F%9B%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A.png 495w,\n/static/d3400496199bdfb0b116a0bd14ba040a/acfc1/%E8%BD%89%E6%8F%9B%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A.png 800w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/d3400496199bdfb0b116a0bd14ba040a/acfc1/%E8%BD%89%E6%8F%9B%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A.png\"\n            alt=\"轉換設定\"\n            title=\"轉換設定\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">轉換設定</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>選擇事件，再輸入事件名稱\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 7vw 0;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 524px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e2b2a94a73a5fc7f013606e3eae6c774/27b27/%E8%BD%89%E6%8F%9B%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.96969696969697%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/e2b2a94a73a5fc7f013606e3eae6c774/a805d/%E8%BD%89%E6%8F%9B%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A2.webp 495w,\n/static/e2b2a94a73a5fc7f013606e3eae6c774/f3a19/%E8%BD%89%E6%8F%9B%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A2.webp 524w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 524px) 100vw, 524px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/e2b2a94a73a5fc7f013606e3eae6c774/b3db0/%E8%BD%89%E6%8F%9B%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A2.png 495w,\n/static/e2b2a94a73a5fc7f013606e3eae6c774/27b27/%E8%BD%89%E6%8F%9B%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A2.png 524w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 524px) 100vw, 524px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/e2b2a94a73a5fc7f013606e3eae6c774/27b27/%E8%BD%89%E6%8F%9B%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A2.png\"\n            alt=\"轉換設定2\"\n            title=\"轉換設定2\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">轉換設定2</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>測試事件，觀看即時轉換是否有數字\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 7vw 0;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2799a11094bee81790364fa689be89f0/acfc1/%E8%BD%89%E6%8F%9B%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30.707070707070706%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/2799a11094bee81790364fa689be89f0/a805d/%E8%BD%89%E6%8F%9B%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A3.webp 495w,\n/static/2799a11094bee81790364fa689be89f0/6ec60/%E8%BD%89%E6%8F%9B%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A3.webp 800w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/2799a11094bee81790364fa689be89f0/b3db0/%E8%BD%89%E6%8F%9B%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A3.png 495w,\n/static/2799a11094bee81790364fa689be89f0/acfc1/%E8%BD%89%E6%8F%9B%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A3.png 800w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/2799a11094bee81790364fa689be89f0/acfc1/%E8%BD%89%E6%8F%9B%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A3.png\"\n            alt=\"轉換設定3\"\n            title=\"轉換設定3\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">轉換設定3</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>完成事件、轉換設定後</h2>\n<p>完成轉換設定之後，我們就可以根據依據轉換數字來判斷，哪個廣告成效較佳、或使用者都在哪個頁面發生轉換。</p>\n<p>如果你對於 javascript 熟悉的話，還可以寫一些動態判斷，例如追蹤某區塊的連結，然後動態帶入連結的標籤名稱、或是頁面，就可以歸納出這區塊中哪些連結使用者最常點擊，哪些最不常點擊等等等等。</p>\n<p>操作廣告的話，我自己是覺得網站設定 ga 事件、轉換後，再搭配 gtm，對於判斷成效有非常大幫助，如果你操作廣告但不會用，那推薦你嘗試看看設定轉換。事件、轉換對於行銷來說是非常好用的 ga 工具，讓你多了一把武器上戰場。</p>\n<!--- ![google analytics](../images/google_analytics.png \"google analytics\") --->\n","fields":{"readingTime":{"text":"8 min read"}},"frontmatter":{"title":"Google analytics 事件追蹤、轉換目標設定教學 ga event","date":"April 25, 2018","description":"Google analytics很重要的事件追蹤，可以使用ga提供的方法ga('send', 'event', xx.xx.xx)來產生事件，成功產生事件後，就可以再把這個事件設定為轉換目標，就可以做到註冊會員、填表等等追蹤了。","categories":"marketing","tags":["google_analytics"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#080808","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/dfeae9b0c0de13cd6ed25543c36e7927/06df8/google_analytics.png","srcSet":"/static/dfeae9b0c0de13cd6ed25543c36e7927/2f882/google_analytics.png 200w,\n/static/dfeae9b0c0de13cd6ed25543c36e7927/ede9b/google_analytics.png 400w,\n/static/dfeae9b0c0de13cd6ed25543c36e7927/06df8/google_analytics.png 800w","sizes":"(min-width: 800px) 800px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/dfeae9b0c0de13cd6ed25543c36e7927/8d68f/google_analytics.webp 200w,\n/static/dfeae9b0c0de13cd6ed25543c36e7927/1056e/google_analytics.webp 400w,\n/static/dfeae9b0c0de13cd6ed25543c36e7927/a1e0e/google_analytics.webp 800w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 800px) 800px, 100vw"}]},"width":1280,"height":411.2}}},"image":{"publicURL":"/static/dfeae9b0c0de13cd6ed25543c36e7927/google_analytics.png"}}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2018-03-interview/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"前端工程師面試心得 | Frontend Engineer interview"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2018-05-reacthoc/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"React Higher Order Components 初探觀念"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"2befcafc-1603-5374-b4ce-16af77febe57","previousPostId":"34f9173d-9df8-57cc-952f-a7633d81dcd9","nextPostId":"fd783194-7e61-5230-8253-754cf62f6e2b"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864","3761976949","441988385"]}